item.title: Curriculum Vitae
item.description: Summary A passionate educator and technology lover with excellent programming and communication skills. Organized and driven with the innate ability to stay on the task. Teaching Experience Monash University, Melbourne (April 2015 - Current) Sessional Lecturer & Teaching Associate (Sessional) Subjects previously taught includes: - FIT1010 - Introduction to Software Engineering - FIT5032 - Internet Applications Development - FIT5042 - Enterprise Web Applications - FIT5120 - Industry Experience Project - FIT5136 - Software Engineering - FIT9131 - Programming Foundations in Java - FIT9134 - Computer Architecture and Operating Systems - FIT9135 - Data Communications
